import React from "react";
import {
  MDBCarousel,
  MDBCarouselInner,
  MDBCarouselItem,
  MDBCarouselElement,
} from "mdb-react-ui-kit";

export default function App() {
  return (
    <MDBCarousel showControls>
      <MDBCarouselInner className="rounded-5 shadow-4-strong">
        <MDBCarouselItem className="active">
          <MDBCarouselElement
            src="https://mdbootstrap.com/img/new/slides/041.webp"
            alt="..."
          />
        </MDBCarouselItem>
        <MDBCarouselItem>
          <MDBCarouselElement
            src="https://mdbootstrap.com/img/new/slides/042.webp"
            alt="..."
          />
        </MDBCarouselItem>
        <MDBCarouselItem>
          <MDBCarouselElement
            src="https://mdbootstrap.com/img/new/slides/043.webp"
            alt="..."
          />
        </MDBCarouselItem>
      </MDBCarouselInner>
    </MDBCarousel>
  );
}
